<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.8">
<l>cārṅkam vaḷaiya valikkun taṭakkaic caturaṉ porutta muṭaiyaṉ</l>
<l>nāṅkaḷem millirun toṭṭiya kaccaṅkam nāṉu mavaṉu maṟitun</l>
<l>tēṅkaṉi māmpoḻiṟ centaḷir kōtuñ ciṟukuyi lētiru mālai</l>
<l>yāṅku viraintollaik kūkiṟṟi yāki lavaṉaināṉ ceyvaṉa kāṇē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The capable [Lord]—with large arms that put pressure on the Śārṅga so that it bent—,</l>
<l rend="indent">He who is suitable:</l>
<l>He and I know of the agreement that we have resolved upon between us being [together].</l>
<l>O little koel that peck the young shoots in the mango groves with sweet ripe fruit!</l>
<l>If you hasten and cry promptly for Tirumāl there, see what I do to Him!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
